FX.name: SlapBackD
FX.description: This delay features a short delay time that is good for muted rhythm playing and rockabilly.

Parameters.name: Time
Parameters.explanation:
Sets the delay time.
When Sync is chosen, the delay time is synchronized to the tempo.

Parameters.name: Mix
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the amount of effected sound that is mixed with the original sound.

Parameters.name: SubDv
Parameters.explanation:
Set the note length of the delay sound.
When P-P is chosen, L/R channels output delays in quarter/dotted eighth notes respectively.
